org.openimaj.image.processing.convolution

Class CLSobel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.image.processing.CLImageAnalyser<FImage>
      • org.openimaj.image.processing.convolution.CLSobel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImageAnalyser<FImage>

    public class CLSobel
extends CLImageAnalyser<FImage>
    OpenCL implementation of a 3x3 Sobel operator. Computes the magnitude, orientation and gradients (in x & y) in parallel.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
